window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b><i>Twelve Mile Limit</i></b><b> by Randy Wayne White is now available for the first time in audio!</b></p> <p><b>\"We'll drop anything we're doing [for] a new Randy White novel and be glad we did.\" (</b><b><i>Denver Post</i></b><b>)</b></p> <p>Randy Wayne White's ninth Doc Ford novel starts out as a fun excursion for four divers off the Florida coast. Two days later only one is found alive - naked atop a light tower in the Gulf of Mexico. What happened during those 48 hours? Doc Ford thinks he's prepared for the truth. He isn't.</p>"; 
